<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well, it is more=C2=A0<em>embarrassing=C2=A0</=
em>to have anything to do with crypto today than it was two weeks ago. Two =
weeks ago, if you were at a traditional financial institution, and you were=
 working on their blockchain project, look, that was a lot less cool than i=
t was in 2017 when everyone launched their blockchain projects, but it was=
=C2=A0<em>fine</em>. =E2=80=9COh right the blockchain project,=E2=80=9D peo=
ple would shrug. Today, less so. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
