<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I feel like =E2=80=9Cupgrade its clearing and =
settlement system to a modern blockchain-based platform=E2=80=9D sounded ve=
ry plausible and cutting-edge in 2015, when this actually launched, but now=
 it has a weirdly retro feel.</p>
