arget=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important;=
 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> CNBC reports</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Grayscale, the asset manager running the world=
=E2=80=99s largest bitcoin fund, said in a statement that it won=E2=80=99t =
share its proof of reserves with customers.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CDue to security concerns, we do not m=
ake such on-chain wallet information and confirmation data publicly availab=
le through a cryptographic Proof-of-Reserve, or other advanced cryptographi=
c accounting procedure,=E2=80=9D said a statement Friday.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Following the implosion of FTX and its subsequ=
ent bankruptcy proceedings exposing that customer funds were missing, multi=
ple crypto exchanges have jumped to release proof-of-reserve audits in orde=
r to assuage investor concerns over the safety of their funds. Others, like=
 Binance, say they soon plan to do so.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Grayscale wrote in a tweet that it realized th=
at failing to disclose a proof of reserves would be a =E2=80=9Cdisappointme=
nt to some,=E2=80=9D but added that a =E2=80=9Cpanic sparked by others is n=
ot a good enough reason to circumvent complex security arrangements=E2=80=
=9D that have kept its investors=E2=80=99 assets =E2=80=9Csafe for years.=
=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is Grayscale=E2=80=99s statement on =E2=
=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29765114.257=
546/aHR0cHM6Ly9ncmF5c2NhbGUuY29tL3NhZmV0eS1zZWN1cml0eS1hbmQtdHJhbnNwYXJlbmN=
5Lw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3d955408" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"=
itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none=
 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Safety, Security, and Transp=
arency</a>=E2=80=9D:=C2=A0</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Due to recent events, investors ar=
e understandably inquiring deeper into their crypto investments. Custody of=
 the digital assets underlying Grayscale=E2=80=99s digital asset products i=
s unaffected, and our products=E2=80=99 digital assets remain safe and secu=
re.=C2=A0</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It links to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/29765114.257546/aHR0cHM6Ly9ncmF5c2NhbGUuY29tL3dwLWNv=
bnRlbnQvdXBsb2Fkcy8yMDIyLzExL0NvaW5iYXNlLVNhZmV0eS1hbmQtU2VjdXJpdHktTGV0dGV=
