nk" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text=
-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color=
: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> frankly hi=
larious amount of pushback</a> from computer scientists saying that this is=
 not at all a trivial problem, that maintaining this list in a way that is =
uniform and consistent and accessible across JPMorgan is hard computer work=
, and that I was being naive in thinking that it=E2=80=99s easy for JPMorga=
n to do arithmetic to its list of dollars. Reading the Celsius examiner=E2=
=80=99s report drives home that they were right. One can=E2=80=99t just wri=
te down a list of account balances and update it for transactions! </p>
